						               													<description>Fairies playing dodgeball with wild magic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A dice game for 2-6 players. Each player takes on the role of a fairy. They gather magic and throw it at members on the opposite team. Fairy's have individual stats and powers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn players take mana tokens from the mana pool, pass their tokens to a teammate, or throw magic at an opponent. Throwing at an opponent entails rolling a number of dice equal to how many mana tokens they have. The game has custom dice with hit icons on 2 of the 6 sides. The attacker compares the number of hits they rolled to the defender's catch value. The defender loses health on a hit, or gathers some of the mana that the attacker spent.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players need to be careful, as the magic is a bit unstable. At the end of each turn the overload die is rolled. Any player whose number comes up on the overload die has to check how much mana they have. If they have too much, their mana explodes causing them to lose health.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
